<div class="faq-sec" data-category="getting-started">
  <h3><span class="ico"><i class="bi bi-rocket-takeoff"></i></span> Getting Started</h3>
  
            <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What is Auto ISP Billing?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down chev"></i></div><div class="faq-a"><p>Auto ISP Billing is a comprehensive software-as-a-service (SaaS) platform designed specifically for Internet Service Providers (ISPs). It automates billing, customer management, payment collection, invoice generation, and integrates with network equipment like MikroTik, RADIUS, Cisco, and Ubiquiti. The platform helps ISPs streamline operations, reduce manual work, and improve customer satisfaction.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How do I get started?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down chev"></i></div><div class="faq-a"><p>Getting started is easy! Simply request a demo from our homepage, and we&rsquo;ll set up a 14-day free trial account for you. No credit card required. During the trial, you&rsquo;ll have access to all features with a limit of 10 test customers. Our support team will guide you through the setup process and help you import your existing customer data.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Do I need technical knowledge to use Auto ISP Billing?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down chev"></i></div><div class="faq-a"><p>No! Auto ISP Billing is designed to be user-friendly and intuitive. While some technical knowledge helps with network integrations (MikroTik, RADIUS), the core billing and customer management features are easy to use. We provide comprehensive documentation, video tutorials, and dedicated support to help you every step of the way.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Can I import my existing customer data?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down chev"></i></div><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes! We support bulk import of customer data via Excel/CSV files. You can import customer details, plans, payment history, and more. Our support team can assist you with data migration to ensure a smooth transition from your current system.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Is there a free trial available?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down chev"></i></div><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes! We offer a 14-day free trial with full access to all features. The trial is limited to 10 test customers and doesn&rsquo;t require any payment information. You can explore all features, test integrations, and see if Auto ISP Billing is the right fit for your business before committing to a paid plan.</p></div></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Billing -->
        <div class="faq-section" data-category="billing">
            <h3><span class="sec-ico"><i class="bi bi-credit-card"></i></span> Billing &amp; Payments</h3>
            <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What subscription plans are available?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down chev"></i></div><div class="faq-a"><p>We offer flexible subscription plans based on your customer count:</p><ul><li><strong>Starter:</strong> Up to 100 customers</li><li><strong>Growth:</strong> Up to 500 customers</li><li><strong>Professional:</strong> Up to 2,000 customers</li><li><strong>Enterprise:</strong> Up to 5,000 customers</li><li><strong>Unlimited:</strong> No customer limit</li></ul><p>All plans include full features. You can upgrade or downgrade anytime based on your needs.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What payment methods do you accept?<i class="bi bi-chevron-down chev"></i></div><div class="faq-a"><p>We accept all major payment methods including Credit/Debit Cards, Net Banking, UPI, and Digital Wallets through our integrated payment gateways (Razorpay, PayU, CCAvenue). All payments are processed securely with 256-bit SSL encryption.</p></div></div>
